data.description: Welcome to the perfect country retreat! Nestled on a sprawling 2.091-acre lot, this charming home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and comfort. Whether you want to sip coffee alone on your back deck or invite some friends over for a game night, this one has room for all your favorite past-times!   The home's 2048 sqft has been thoughtfully laid out to provide ample living, kitchen, and dining spaces plus 3 bedrooms, including an oversized master and master bath. The workshop with electricity is the perfect place for working on your projects, and the large barn is a great place to store your yard implements and equipment or even house a few of your favorite small farm animals.   Country living doesn't get much cuter this one. Schedule your showing today!
